<!-- What Drives Me -->
<section class="about-section" data-animate>
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="about-section__label">// what drives me</p>
    <h2 class="about-section__title">What Drives Me</h2>
    <p>I believe the best institutional communications are honest, crafted, and human. Whether I'm redesigning a flagship website, producing a video about student makers, or writing copy about why engineering matters — the goal is always the same: help people understand something true about a place, and make them feel something real about it.</p>
    <p><strong>I care about clarity over cleverness, listening before building, and making work that lasts.</strong></p>
  </div>
